high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the large round table
Pick up the plate nearest the edge of the table
Turn around and walk over to the microwave above the oven
Put the plate in the microwave, turn it on, then remove it
Turn around and walk over to the small dark table in the corner right of the door
Put the plate down on the small dark table
anns.task_desc: Put the hot plate on the small dark table

high_descs: Take a right, walk to circular table
Pick up plate closest to the edge
open microwave, turn on microwave, remove plate
Turn around, walk to door, take a right
Walk to table, set plate down on black table
anns.task_desc: Heat up plate to place on table

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black table.
Pick up the plate closest to you.
Turn around and hang left to the microwave.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Turn around and walk forward and to the right to the black table in the corner.
Place the plate on the right front corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate on a table.
